Package: ggfocus
Type: Package
Title: Special Scales that Focus Specific Levels in your ggplot()
Version: 1.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Victor", "Fregugglia", email = "victorfreguglia@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
BugReports: https://github.com/Freguglia/ggfocus/issues
URL: https://github.com/Freguglia/ggfocus
Description: A 'ggplot2' extension that provides tools for automatically
    creating scales that helps focusing on subgroups of the data plotted 
    without removing the less important information.
